title: Meet Tim Duncan: Australian football's new best player
text:
Updated Oct 8, 2015 at 2:26a ET 
San Antonio Spurs center Tim Duncan is probably great at every sport in the entire world. This is the only rational assumption one can make after watching this video, wherein Duncan successfully boots an Australian football towards a door. true A video posted by @sundaddy12 on Oct 7, 2015 at 2:16pm PDT 
If it doesn't sound or look super impressive, that's probably because you don't understand the complex strategy and masterful sense that goes into doing what Duncan just did. 
Hear that sound? It's a collective exhale from every Spurs fan in the world, thanking the basketball gods that Duncan wasn't born in Australia. If he was, there's no doubt who their greatest football player would be today. 
And San Antonio would most definitely not have five championship trophies to its name. MORE NEWS: Want stories delivered to you? Sign up for our NBA newsletters.
